VALUES
  ('public-health-specialist-moex-01197', 'public-health-specialist', 'public-health-specialist-moex-113-8041b019', 'sub-public-health-specialist-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '高血壓研究的一個重要假設，是透過鈉攝取限制以降低血壓。其研究人員召集8個人參加一 個鈉攝取限制研究，量測其原本的鈉攝取當作基線（baseline）及接受一週飲食諮詢之後的鈉 攝取，資料如下表。以符號檢定（signtest）來檢定一週飲食諮詢是否能有效降低鈉攝取，檢 定結果的p值為下列何者？ Person 1 2 3 4 5 6 7 8 Average s.d. Baseline 14 12 22 14 18 42 16 14 19 9.798 Week1 10 24 16 20 16 32 12 14 18 7.709 Difference 4 -12 6 -6 2 10 4 0 1 7.010', '["0.0078", "0.1250", "0.2266", "0.4322"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:58+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "d5bdd3295981", "answer_pdf_sha1": "45e351b5915d", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113100", "c": "108", "s": "0802", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "生物統計學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、113年專技人員高等考試心理師、法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛...", "original_question_number": 9, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "publichealth", "db_exam_id": "public-health-specialist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('public-health-specialist-moex-01198', 'public-health-specialist', 'public-health-specialist-moex-113-8041b019', 'sub-public-health-specialist-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '承上題，若以其他無母數方法來檢定一週飲食諮詢是否能有效降低鈉攝取，下列何者正確？', '["採Wilcoxon符號等級檢定（Wilcoxonsigned-ranktest），正等級和R+=16.5", "採Wilcoxon符號等級檢定，正等級和=68", "採Wilcoxon等級和檢定（Wilcoxonrank-sumtest），其中一組等級和W =68 1", "採Wilcoxon等級和檢定，其中一組序等級W =16.5 1"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:58+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "d5bdd3295981", "answer_pdf_sha1": "45e351b5915d", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113100", "c": "108", "s": "0802", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "生物統計學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、113年專技人員高等考試心理師、法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛...", "original_question_number": 10, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "publichealth", "db_exam_id": "public-health-specialist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('public-health-specialist-moex-01199', 'public-health-specialist', 'public-health-specialist-moex-113-8041b019', 'sub-public-health-specialist-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '為研究一氧化碳暴露對於冠狀動脈疾病的影響，某研究從三個醫學中心招募男性參與者，首先進 行基線特徵檢查，以確保來自不同中心的男性是可比較的。接著測量參與者的肺功能之第 1 秒 用力呼氣體積（FEV），得到A中心20位參與者的平均FEV 為2.63、標準差0.49；B中心15', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:58+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "d5bdd3295981", "answer_pdf_sha1": "45e351b5915d", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113100", "c": "108", "s": "0802", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "生物統計學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、113年專技人員高等考試心理師、法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛...", "original_question_number": 11, "answer_corrected": true, "flags": ["answer_corrected_skip_v1", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "publichealth", "db_exam_id": "public-health-specialist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
